@startuml
' Generated: 2026-03-07 | Phase: 3 | Status: AS-BUILT
title Event Polling (Daemon -> Chain)

participant "Daemon" as daemon
participant "EventPoller" as poller
participant "Sui RPC" as rpc
database "Cursor File\n(.cursors/*.json)" as cursor

== Initialization ==

daemon -> poller : new EventPoller(\n  packageId, module, pollingIntervalMs)
daemon -> poller : start(handler)
poller -> cursor : load last cursor (or null)

== Polling Loop ==

loop every pollingIntervalMs
  poller -> rpc : queryEvents(\n  MoveModule { package, module },\n  cursor, limit=50, descending=false)
  rpc --> poller : { data: SuiEvent[], nextCursor }

  loop for each event
    poller -> daemon : handler(event)
    daemon -> daemon : process event\n(update state, log, score)
  end

  poller -> cursor : save nextCursor
end

note right of poller
  CP Daemon polls 3 modules:
  - relay_registry
  - control_plane_registry
  - room_manager

  Validator Daemon polls:
  - validator_registry
end note

@enduml
